x 21px; display: block; background-color: #ececec;\">This site is a demo site only. This product is not available for sale at our site. <br />But you can buy it at <a href=\"http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-3652263-10356324?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkgeek.com%2Fgeektoys%2Frc%2Fb8ab%2F%3Fref%3Dc\" target=\"_top\">ThinkGeek.com</a><img src=\"http://www.tqlkg.com/image-3652263-10356324\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />, this is where we took description from.</div>', `price` = '59.99', `sale_price` = '59.99', `sku` = '00095', `weight` = '1.0', `image` = 'demo_store_p159704.jpeg', `image_height` = '500', `image_width` = '378', `image_type` = 'image/jpeg', `image_size` = '80309', `image_source` = 'F', `thumbnail` = 'demo_store_t159704.jpeg', `thumbnail_width` = '68', `thumbnail_height` = '90', `thumbnail_size` = '2689', `thumbnail_type` = 'image/jpeg', `thumbnail_source` = 'F';
